item.title: RSS end-of-life
item.description:
Since none really was reading my RSS feed, I'm shutting it down. To whoever reads this: whoever you are, you were the only reader of my RSS feed. Please write me an email ('alexey.shpakovsky.ru'.replace('.','@')) and I'll keep you updated on all updates.
I've switched to a new static-site generator, which is faster then bashblog, but has less features - no RSS, for example.
item.dc:creator: Alexey Shpakovsky
